Over the years I created one and another website for a specific task.
Today there are plenty of websites currently up and running.

The idea of this site is to (sooner or later) consolidate some of the following ones:

* [My very old personal website](http://nico.schotteli.us/)
* [My old personal website (being merged into this one)](http://nico.schottelius.org/)
* [UNIX related projects](http://unix.schottelius.org/)
* [irc related data/information](http://irc.schottelius.org/)
* The public [mailing lists](http://l.schottelius.org) hosted on ***l.schottelius.org***.

## This website

This website is generated using the [ikiwiki software](http://www.ikiwiki.info).
Its source is maintained via [git](http://git-scm.com/) and can be found
in [gitweb](http://git.schottelius.org/?p=netzseiten/www.nico.schottelius.org;a=summary)
and cloned via

    git clone git://git.schottelius.org/netzseiten/www.nico.schottelius.org

